<plot>A Behind the Scenes look at the events that surrounded the trial against the KING OF POP! Including original Michael Jackson footage, and Cameo Appearances: Kanye West, Ashford &amp; Simpson, Mo'Nique, Kim Whitley, Billy Gibbons of ZZ Top, Dorien Wilson, Yolanda Adams, Jon Voight, Fantasia, Shemar Moore and Terry Lewis. Plus commentary on Chris Tucker, Macauley Culkin and Debbie Rowe's courtroom testimony. See who was voted the Most Hated Media Pundits. A tale of a fight at Neverland's gate. Also features Geraldine Hughes (author of Redemption) &amp; J. Randy Taraborelli (author of The Magic and the Madness). And see our own Michael Jackson Music Video.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?063840</url></doc>
